{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_04_02",
  "title": "fran 2話 なんだ蛇か",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――サバイバル開始",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Survival started",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1266.6666667,
          "startTime": 1.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "よし、この辺りは食べられる植物が沢山ありますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ there are plenty of edible plants around here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.5666667263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですか？　凄いですね……\n俺にはどれが食べられるのかさっぱりです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? That's amazing…\nI have no idea which ones are edible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.1333331267,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.0850796818
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "教えてあげてもいいですけど、質問一つにつき\n救助費として一万円を請求しますからね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I could tell you‚ but I'll charge you\n$60 per question as a rescue fee.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.3666672865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "こういう時は助け合うんじゃないんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aren't we supposed to help each other in times like this!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.705509293,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.5462348897
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "助け合うにしても、一方的に私が情報を渡すだけに\nなるじゃないですか。それはフェアじゃないですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even in helping‚ it’s not fair\nif I'm the only one giving information.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.8333326815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "お腹を壊すことなく、それなりに美味しく食べられる\n植物の情報を教える……お安くは出来ませんよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sharing information about edible plants that\nwon’t make you sick isn’t cheap‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.3999993482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.5000000794
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "い、今は持ち合わせがなくてですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I… I don't have any money on me right now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.0578900933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.4916037997
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん？　まぁ、私の散策が長過ぎたのが\n原因でこうなったところはありますし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh? Well‚ it’s partly my fault for\nwandering around too long…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.8999942619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "仕方ないですから、今回のサバイバル情報で\n迷惑掛けた分をチャラにするってことで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ I'll let this survival info make up for\nthe trouble I caused.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.1666634718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.440968144
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、でも……{user}さんは勝手に\nついて来ただけだし、やっぱり請求していいのかも？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But then again… since {user}-san followed me here‚\nmaybe I should still charge you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.499993499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.9401516717
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ですから、franさん一人を\n無人島に置いてなんて行けませんって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I couldn't just leave fran-san alone\non an deserted island!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.599993499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "分かりましたよ、仕方ないから教えてあげます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ alright‚ I'll tell you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.1841225108,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.7494510453
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "まずこれは……ツルナですね\nハマホウレンソウなんて名前でも知られています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First‚ this is called New Zealand spinach.\nIt's also known as beach spinach.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.9333293755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "癖がなく調理がしやすくて、おひたしや炒め物\n汁物にも使われることが多いですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's mild‚ easy to cook‚ and often used in salads‚\nstir-fries‚ and soups.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.6666627089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.6159815272
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "それからこっちはハマダイコン\n大根が野生化したものなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And this one here is beach radish.\nIt’s a wild radish.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.9666627089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.4708341401
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "味は辛味が強くて土臭いらしくて\nこれはまぁ……どうしてもお腹が空いたら食べましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It has a strong spicy flavor and a bit of an earthy taste.\nWell‚ let's save this one for when we're really hungry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.6666627089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.1246437829
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　あれはヤマモモですよ！\n生で食べられる上に甘酸っぱくてとても美味しいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! That's Raspberry!\nYou can eat it raw‚ and it's sweet and sour‚ really delicious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.1333293755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.6060938319
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "高い所にあるので\n{user}さんに頑張ってもらいましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's high up‚\nso {user}-san‚ you'll have to do your best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.3666616916,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "甘いものは貴重ですから、気合いを入れて下さいね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sweet things are precious‚ so give it your all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.9471145909,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "わ、分かりました\nええと、どこに足をかけるといいかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I understand.\nUm‚ where should I step…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.9666622002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.5208970349
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "franさんのおかげで食べ物がかなり採れましたね\nこれならなんとか――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to fran-san‚ we've gathered a lot of food.\nWith this‚ we should be able to manage――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.2333227634,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7000.0106493999965,
          "startTime": 140.2333334128
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1300.0106494000079,
          "startTime": 134.5333334128
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.5328520735
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "しっ！　静かに\n……あっちから音が聞こえる。行きましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shh! Be quiet.\n…I hear something from over there. Let's go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.6999965508,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6683.451903000019,
          "startTime": 143.3834484538
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6450.118569700009,
          "startTime": 143.1501151205
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.9167817872
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "こんな所に湧き水が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's a spring here…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.6501120688,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_02-kor017.m4a",
      "text": "飲み水はこの場所で確保しましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We'll secure our drinking water here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.3081619224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
